onsortium comprising columbia university george washington university indiana university stanford university and the university of british columbia each university will host two fellows each year for five years starting in september 2006 html+ read more please see the ksp fellowships page for details and application forms http ksp stanford edu fellowships search aparc search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages news of interest posco ngo fellowship program ended after three years august 20 2009 ksp news korean studies program welcomes visiting fellows and scholars for 2008 2009 academic year july 23 2008 ksp announcement posco ngo fellowship committee admitted 10 applicants for 2008 fellowship program may 14 2008 ksp announcement korean ngo activities and perspectives for a better world april 28 2008 ksp news posco ngo fellowship committee admitted 10 applicants for 2007 fellowship program may 9 2007 ksp announcement announcing the posco ngo fellowship program for 2007 2008 december 13 2006 ksp news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 9741 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
